{"tid":1857822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職工盟：將會成立「行動基金」支援工會成員","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T12:44:48.000Z","uid":125168,"like":186,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"01dd5460c7a561e4473cbfe38d03e80fa9870be4","tid":1857822,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"香港職工會聯盟吳敏兒：<br />\n真正嘅逃兵係令香港中門大開嘅人！<br />\n<br />\n醫護人員終年被道德綁架，香港人要全力為大家爭取封關，才能真正保障自己。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是次為醫護的大團體，真正為香港人的生命作出決戰！<br />\n<br />\n其他打工仔女都要在自己的職場抗爭起來！</span>工會將會成立「行動基金」，去應對被秋後算帳的會員，職工盟會借出戶口作收款。<br />\n<br />\n2月4日，我們已連結55名區議員作支持的聯署。<br />\n<br />\nfrom <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ad7fe980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a>"},{"pid":"6bcdad729464ae0a8cec201954f773d9f91f6842","tid":1857822,"uid":125168,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6K3mTV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6K3mTV.gif&h=b42186d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc9070160a476c97bccd810f4c79f0e7208347f5","tid":1857822,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e9d82fb9ec264c4351b02092f0ee6be825d73e","tid":1857822,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全面反擊啦，仲唔入工會嘅你諗緊乜？</span><br />\n<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9Bvk